---

<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-28 border-y border-border bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column: Avatar and Stats -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-end gap-6">
        <div class="relative w-64 h-64 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 lg:w-80 lg:h-80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-border bg-gradient-to-tr from-accent/15 via-transparent to-primary/5 flex items-center justify-center group">
          <!-- Glassmorphism overlay glow -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-accent to-blue-400 opacity-10 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          
          <!-- Monogram Logo Initials -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center">
            <span class="text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-widest text-accent font-heading select-none drop-shadow-sm">SK</span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mt-2 font-semibold">Srikar Kukkadapu</span>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Outer border shine -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white/10 dark:border-white/5 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat pills -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center w-full lg:justify-end max-w-sm lg:max-w-none">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-background border border-border rounded-xl shadow-sm text-center flex-grow sm:flex-grow-0">
            <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground block uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Grade</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent">8.74 CGPA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-background border border-border rounded-xl shadow-sm text-center flex-grow sm:flex-grow-0">
            <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground block uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Degree</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-accent">B.Tech AI & DS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Biography Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-2 block">About Me</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-primary leading-tight">
            Passionate about building systems that think.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm a Computer Science student specializing in Artificial Intelligence and Data Science at Velagapudi Ramakrishna Siddhartha Engineering College, Vijayawada. I build production-grade AI systems, intelligent backends, and full-stack platforms that solve real-world problems.
          </p>
          <p>
            My work spans multi-tenant FastAPI backends, LangGraph-powered agentic pipelines, ML-driven prediction engines, and cross-platform mobile apps. I focus on clean architecture, scalable design, and measurable impact.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not building, I'm exploring emerging LLM research, competing in hackathons, and contributing to open-source projects.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Facts grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/60">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <span class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
            <span>Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <span class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">🎓</span>
            <span>B.Tech CSE (AI & DS) — June 2027</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <span class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">💼</span>
            <span>Open to internships & full-time roles</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <span class="text-lg leading-none" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>
            <span>Python · FastAPI · LLMs · ML</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
